{"tid":687722,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"梁振英：強烈譴責中共當權者血腥屠殺中國人","createTime":"2018-06-02T13:25:26.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-05T02:08:15.000Z","uid":2054,"like":47,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"d2ff82fa5c87f3903b91122377bb347b440fb5a0","tid":687722,"uid":2054,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-02T13:25:26.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20140604/18744251\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20140604%2F18744251&d=MByN8l5tr7paOzoQpA3Ku4zZXVCnaYNE8CBFJ%2F%2FgXXY%3D&h=b19d25c6\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20140604%2F18744251&h=86861086\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20140604/18744251</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/02/212322_fc00077f789ce568b695730dee63099d.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F02%2F212322_fc00077f789ce568b695730dee63099d.png&h=579fe7b7&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"dbd348b83b6cff32af0dc40dd76e460dbdb990e6","tid":687722,"uid":2054,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-02T13:31:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20111025/large/25la6p2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20111025%2Flarge%2F25la6p2.jpg&h=ce9eba1d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20111025/15736460\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20111025%2F15736460&d=MByN8l5tr7paOzoQpA3Ku4zZXVCnaYNE8CBFJ%2F%2FgXXY%3D&h=9c7f04ff\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20111025%2F15736460&h=83a3c969\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20111025/15736460</a><br />\n<br />\n梁振英不同時期六四言論<br />\n<br />\n1989年6月7日<br />\n聯同一群財經界人士在報章刊登聲明，表明「我們強烈譴責北京當局濫殺市民的冷血暴行，並沉痛哀悼為民主進步的中國而犧牲的愛國同胞。」<br />\n<br />\n去年11月<br />\n出席一論壇時形容六四是中國人一場悲劇，堅稱未清楚六四事件所有真相，並指「如果有一個中國人要攞諾貝爾和平獎，我有一點唔太明白，點解第一個攞諾貝爾和平獎嘅人，唔係鄧小平先生？」<br />\n<br />\n昨天<br />\n拒評是否支持平反六四，強調在此問題上「立場同以前一樣，唔再補充」"},{"pid":"34ee490df8a8312db54a7d8592986ca9767a3c27","tid":687722,"uid":34103,"like":3,"dislike":17,"score":-14,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-02T13:32:18.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"e6deaec96e77d66ef40293d0da685e8476f0f5a7","tid":687722,"uid":9193,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-02T13:32:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5b0ee3fd82092e637ac6b3a2463f7df375c79643","tid":687722,"uid":78347,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-02T13:32:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4de8e13a1e32ef1f0ead36d66642041860ffddf1","tid":687722,"uid":139700,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-02T13:34:20.000Z","msg":"毓民好似講過，分分鐘做政協前寫咗悔過書。其他奶共分分鐘都係呢?"},{"pid":"3b427e53da91e0e7342fffbe82fcf8e53f9ac30f","tid":687722,"uid":79410,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"34ee490df8a8312db54a7d8592986ca9767a3c27","tid":687722,"uid":34103,"like":3,"dislike":17,"score":-14,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-02T13:32:18.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-02T13:37:06.000Z","msg":"不嬲都係出賣親人朋友搵得最多."},{"pid":"cc0816c9ecb5fc6413523d5a9b2c8bd218722415"